      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a superior balance of performance and value. Meticulously maintained and presented in excellent mechanical order, it offers the discerning driver a sophisticated experience. The exterior retains its original luster, while the interior reflects a high standard of care. Fully inspected and ready for immediate delivery, this motorcar is a testament to quality engineering and responsible ownership.",
