    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in great shape for all your upcoming adventures! It drives super smoothly and has been really well-taken care of. If you're looking for something dependable and comfy, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
