      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s high-revving peak. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that delivers a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and transmitted through a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure chassis longevity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the cooling system has been overhauled with an aluminum radiator. The suspension maintains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the communicative steering and lateral stability enthusiasts demand. A well-sorted driver's car with its critical preventative maintenance items addressed.",
      "price": 32500.0,
